quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  14,22,"Seytaane wi'a, tuma fiyaaku on √Īaawaa: \"Pellet Alla fodiino on fodoore goonga; mi fodi on mi lunndii on. Alanaa lam e mo'on immorde e hujja, si wanaa mi nodii on, on jaabike lam. Wata on felam; felee ko'e mon. Wanaa mi faabotoo…óo on; wanaa on faabotoo…ďe lam. Mi yeddii ko kafiduno…óon mi kon [e Alla] ado (hannde)\". Pellet, too√Īoo…ďe …ďen, hino woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  14,23,"Gom…óim…ďe golli mo∆ī∆īu…ói …ďen naatnaa e Aljannaaji, can…ói hino ila ley majji, ko …ďe duumoray…ďe ton e duŇčayee Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Hiwraandu ma…ď…ďe ndun ton ko: \"Salaam\" (Kisiyee). @Corrected"
  14,24,"E a yi'aali ko honno Alla piyiri misal konngol laa…ďungol, ko wano leggal welngal, binndeere maggal ko tabitu…ói, cal…ói maggal no ka weeyo"
  14,25,"Hingal okkira dim…óe maggal on tuma kala, e duŇčayee Joomi maggal. Alla no piyana yim…ďe …ďen mise, belajo'o …ďe waajitoto"
  14,26,"Ko woni kadi misal konngol so…ďungol, ko wano leggal so…ďungal, irtaangal ka hoore-leydi, ngal alanaa …óum √Īii…ďirde"
  14,27,"Alla no tabintinira gom…óim…ďe …ďen konngol tabitungol, ka nguurandam aduna e ka laakara. Alla no majjina too√Īoo…ďe …ďen. Alla no wa…óa ko O muuyi"